    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good summary of the regulatory side. But I'm also hearing a lot from the tech companies themselves and some industry analysts saying these moves are actually pretty shortsighted. What's the counter-argument to all this? Like, how are the companies defending themselves against these claims?",
